thread.title: TMJ can lead FAM to excellence again, says Salahuddin
thread.title_full: TMJ can lead FAM to excellence again, says Salahuddin

title: TMJ can lead FAM to excellence again, says Salahuddin
text:
The crown prince of Johor Tunku Ismail Sultan Ibrahim can lead the Football Association Malaysia (FAM) to success as he has a good track record, said Amanah deputy president Salahuddin Ayub. 
"I am confident that the Johor crown prince should be given the chance to lead FAM. 
"My choice is not based on the fact that I am a Johorean but as a Malaysian, I see that he has a track record to be proud of," Salahuddin said in a statement today.
